@startuml svc-scheduling-orchestrator--post-schedule-requests

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #2E86AB
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4F8
    LifeLineBorderColor #A23B72
    BoxBorderColor #F18F01
    BoxBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
    NoteBorderColor #c77b30
    NoteBackgroundColor #FEF3E7
}

header [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/#integration-context ⬆ svc-scheduling-orchestrator Integration Context]]

title POST /schedule-requests\nRequest optimal schedule for a trip

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #DBEAFE
participant "svc-scheduling-orchestrator" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/]] #E8F4F8
participant "Guide Mgmt" as GM [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Trail Mgmt" as TM [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Weather Svc" as WX [[/microservices/svc-weather/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Trip Catalog" as TC [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #FFF8F0
database "PG + Valkey" as DB #FCE4EC

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-scheduling-orchestrator.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /schedule-requests
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> GM : [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/#get-guidesguide_idavailability-get-guide-availability-windows Check guide availability]]
activate GM #DBEAFE
GM --> Svc : OK
deactivate GM

Svc -> TM : [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#get-trailstrail_idconditions-get-current-trail-conditions Verify trail conditions]]
activate TM #DBEAFE
TM --> Svc : OK
deactivate TM

Svc -> WX : [[/microservices/svc-weather/#get-weatherforecast-get-weather-forecast Get forecast]]
activate WX #DBEAFE
WX --> Svc : OK
deactivate WX

Svc -> TC : [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/#get-tripstrip_id-get-trip-details Get trip details]]
activate TC #DBEAFE
TC --> Svc : OK
deactivate TC

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Notify assigned guides]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml